    MyBidsActivity

    This activity shows one of the current user's available items (selected in MyItemsActivity).
    MyItemsActivity
    This activity allows a user to see their items that are available to be rented out (items NOT bidded or borrowed).
    MyProfileViewActivity
    This activity shows the user their profile information which can then be edited (using longClick) as well as the options to view their items (MyItemsActivity), view items of theirs with bids on them (MyBidsActivity), view items they are renting out (ViewBorrowingOutActivity), view all bids on their items (IncomingBidsActivity), view items they are currently borrowing (MyBorrowedItemsActivity) and search for things to borrow (SearchResultsActivity).
